{
  "id": "RAW_c66a9c",
  "title": "多模态上新｜阶跃星辰开源 3D 大模型 Step1X-3D",
  "url": "http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNTYxNzg5Mg==&mid=2247485684&idx=1&sn=8672972b947196abfa28d4ba56a68189",
  "date": "2025-05-14 07:44:00",
  "author": "拥抱开源的",
  "siteName": "阶跃星辰",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">上周我们发布了音跃模型 ACE-Step，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-weight: bold;\">今天阶跃在多模态方向上再迈坚实一步，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">正式发布并开源 3D 大模型——Step1X-3D</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">，这是继图像、视频、语音、音乐等模态后，我们在多模态方向的最新</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">成果</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step1X-3D 模型总参数量达 4.8B（几何模块 1.3B，纹理模块 3.5B），凭借坚实的数据基础与先进的 3D 原生架构，可生成</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">高保真、可控</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的 3D 内容。</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step1X-3D 不止于视觉“好看”，更追求实现“好用”与“可控”</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，旨在为 3D 内容创作提供强大而可靠的技术引擎。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3985608540831350787\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3985608540831350787\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F0LDJQiaWfxzl8ic2s9kjjsmib0OBzlSAvfZdkprsG4REdudZasfbuJvicuwIHuUFCiaRo9HPlb6Sc1zbvruPc7ejQEQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></iframe></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin: 16px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们公布了完整的数据清洗策略，数据预处理策略，以及&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">800K&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">高质量的&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3D&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">资产，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3D VAE</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">、</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3D</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">geometry Diffusion&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">以及&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">texture Diffusion&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的全链路训练代码开源，助力&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3D&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">生成社区发展。</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;fon