eaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:0px;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;margin-right:0px;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:0px;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;margin-right:0px;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-style: italic;\">https://www.modelscope.cn/models/stepfun-ai/Step1X-3D</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:0px;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;margin-right:0px;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">Tech Report：</span></span><em style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:0px;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;margin-right:0px;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></em></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 32px;\"><em style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:0px;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;margin-right:0px;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-style: italic;\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2505.07747</span></span></em></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:40px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-weight: bold;\">核心特性与技术支撑</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step1X-3D 尝试解决 3D 内容生成的关键挑战，在数据、生成质量与可控性上进行了创新实践。</span></span></p>\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 32px 8px 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size:18px;\">1、数据驱动与算法协同优化</span></span></strong></h4>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">好数据是好模型的基础。Step1X-3D 对超 500 万原始数据进行严格筛选与处理后，建立了</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">包含 200 万高质量、标准化的训练样本库，</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">有效克服了行业数据稀缺与质量参差的瓶颈。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 24px 8px 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"288\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100002018\" data-ratio=\"0.4981481481481482\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bf52cc84-b268-4598-07ff-8e8fa71f3800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bf52cc84-b268-4598-07ff-8e8fa71f3800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">数据处理流程示意图</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此外，Step1X-3D 通过增强型网格-SDF 转换技术等方法，从源头保障了模型学习的精准性与最终生成的高效性，让水密几何转换成功率提升了 20%，也让 Step1X-3D 拥有了强大的泛化能力与细节捕捉力。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 16px 8px 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"743\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100002019\" data-ratio=\"1.2859116022099448\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6b10561d-07d1-4c83-f76e-5edca83fdd00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"724\" style=\"width: 319px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6b10561d-07d1-4c83-f76e-5edca83fdd00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Step1X-3D 数据筛选与 SDF 转换流程示意图</span></span></p>\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 32px 8px 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size:18px;\">2、3D 原生生成：结构清晰、细节生动</span></span></strong></h4>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step1X-3D 采用先进的 3D 原生两阶段架构，解耦几何与纹理表征，确保生成的不仅是视觉“皮囊”，更是结构可靠、可供下游应用的“骨架”，有效规避几何失真，保证生成的准确性、真实感与一致性。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 24px 8px 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"149\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100002020\" data-ratio=\"0.2574074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4176ec50-d493-44d5-2ab3-245b69c4b500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4176ec50-d493-44d5-2ab3-245b69c4b500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Step1X-3D 的原生 3D 架构</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 24px 8px 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"314\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100002021\" data-ratio=\"0.5594965675057209\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/836fb29f-a0dd-4e63-95ba-ea4a57d87700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"874\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/836fb29f-a0dd-4e63-95ba-ea4a57d87700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px 8px 32px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">几何生成模型基于 FLUX MMDiT 结构和 Rectified flow 算法直接对 3D 表示生成进行建模</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"302\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100002022\" data-ratio=\"0.5222222222222223\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a2b90465-b884-4303-5070-e00f8ed0a300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a2b90465-b884-4303-5070-e00f8ed0a300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <ul style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 1.5em;margin:0px 8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\"></ul>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">纹理生成模型基于预训练的 Diffusion model，通过单视图和 3D 几何信息指导，生成多视角一致的纹理信息</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 1.5em;margin:0px 8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 24px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.6em;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 [&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ul&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.544px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;}]\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">几何塑形更精准</span></span></strong></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">几何生成的核心在于采用</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为 3D 特性深度优化的创新混合 VAE-DiT 架构</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。该架构负责生成 TSDF 内部表示，确保产出的 3D 模型结构完整、无破面漏点；同时通过引入锐利边缘采样（Sharp Edge Sampling）等技术，精准捕捉并还原物体的丰富几何细节。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 24px 8px 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"315\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100002023\" data-ratio=\"0.5611111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4942199e-1e80-4f50-8e28-8b177d46c800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4942199e-1e80-4f50-8e28-8b177d46c800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">几何示例：覆盖硬边与曲面结构</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 1.5em;margin:0px 8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 24px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">纹理细节更生动</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">纹理生成则基于强大的 SD-XL 模型进行深度定制与优化。通过几何条件（利用法线与位置信息）的精准引导，以及潜在空间多视图同步技术，实现了与几何模块的高效协同。确保生成的纹理不仅色彩饱满、质感生动逼真，更能跨越多视图保持高度一致，与复杂三维表面精密贴合，有效避免常见的扭曲与接缝瑕疵。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"244\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100002024\" data-ratio=\"0.4222222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f786ce92-a90d-4fc4-38cb-b883e70c3100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f786ce92-a90d-4fc4-38cb-b883e70c3100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 8px 8px 24px; text-align: center;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">纹理示例：呈现清晰一致的表面纹理</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 32px 8px 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size:18px;\">3、控制简单、效果可调</span></span></strong></h4>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step1X-3D 显著提升了 3D 内容生成的可控性与易用性。其关键在于，VAE-Diffusion 整体架构在设计上与主流 2D 生成模型（如 Stable Diffusion）保持了高度一致性，从而能够无缝引入并应用成熟的 2D 控制技术（如轻量化的 LoRA 微调）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">因此用户可以对生成 3D 资产的对称性、表面细节（如锋利度、平滑度）等多种属性进行直观、精细的调控，让创作更精准地符合用户意图。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 24px 8px 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"227\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100002029\" data-ratio=\"0.4046296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4cebbc9f-e019-4f55-9d61-6b9af8cf9800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4cebbc9f-e019-4f55-9d61-6b9af8cf9800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">对比图 1：对称性控制效果</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 24px 8px 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d6226b2f-e4b6-4bae-5575-496a46d93b00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.34444444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"199\" data-imgfileid=\"100002030\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d6226b2f-e4b6-4bae-5575-496a46d93b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">对</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">比图 2：表面细节控制效果（锋利/平滑</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">）</span></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:40px 8px 32px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-weight: bold;\">性能评估</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了客观评估 Step1X-3D 的实际效果，我们通过一个自建的综合测试（包含 110 个多样化测试用例），对 Step1X-3D 进行了严格的定量与定性评估，同时与多款主流模型进行全面对比。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">结果显示：在自动评估中，Step1X-3D 在多项关键维度上均表现出色。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"546\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100002032\" data-ratio=\"0.9722222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/030cecfe-beca-42ec-f780-25cd54596000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/030cecfe-beca-42ec-f780-25cd54596000/public\"></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在与主流 3D 模型的对比评测中，特别是在衡量内容与输入语义一致性的核心指标 CLIP-Score 上，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Step1X-3D 取得了当前所有对比模型中的最高分</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，为开源社区提供了极具竞争力的 3D 生成方案。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"210\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100002031\" data-ratio=\"0.3638888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/61b52a82-f542-43d2-378c-c26ccce0e100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/61b52a82-f542-43d2-378c-c26ccce0e100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">不同 3D 模型测评对比数据</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">欢迎大家上手体验！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px 8px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:15px;\">Online Demo：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin: 0px 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:0px;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;margin-right:0px;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-style: italic;\">https://huggingface.co/spaces/stepfun-ai/Step1X-3D</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "阶跃星辰开源多模态 3D 大模型 Step1X-3D，提供高保真、可控的 3D 内容生成能力，并开放 800K 高质量 3D 资产和全链路训练代码",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "阶跃星辰开源多模态 3D 大模型 Step1X-3D，提供高保真、可控的 3D 内容生成能力，并开放 800K 高质量 3D 资产和全链路训练代码",
  "summary": "文章介绍了阶跃星辰最新开源的多模态 3D 大模型 Step1X-3D，该模型总参数量达 4.8B(几何模块 1.3B，纹理模块 3.5B)，专注于 3D 内容生成的高保真度和可控性。文章详细阐述了模型的数据驱动策略，包括从 500 万原始数据中筛选出 200 万高质量训练样本，以及采用的增强型网格-SDF 转换技术(提升水密几何转换成功率 20%)。模型采用创新的 3D 原生两阶段架构，解耦几何与纹理表征：几何生成采用优化的 VAE-DiT 架构，纹理生成基于定制的 SD-XL 模型，确保内容结构可靠且细节生动。此外，文章展示了模型在可控性方面的优势，如支持对称性和表面细节的精细调控。阶跃星辰还开源了 800K 高质量 3D 资产和全链路训练代码，助力 3D 生成社区发展。评估显示 Step1X-3D 在 CLIP-Score 等关键指标上表现优异，为开源社区提供了极具竞争力的 3D 生成方案。",
